Package: MacBehaviour
Type: Package
Title: Behavioural studies of large language models
Version: 1.1.0
Author: Xufeng Duan, Shixuan Li, Zhenguang Cai
Maintainer: Shixuan Li <shixuanli@cuhk.edu.hk>
Description: This package provides an efficient way to design and conduct psycholinguistic experiments for testing the performance of LLM. It simplifies the process of setting up experiments, and data collection via OpenAI API, facilitating a smooth workflow for researchers in the field of machine behaviour.
License: LGPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: false
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5.0),
    openxlsx,
    httr,
    dplyr,
    rjson
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    roxygen2
